Package: erlang-mochiweb
Source: mochiweb
Version: 2.18.0-1
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Laszlo Boszormenyi (GCS) <gcs@debian.org>
Installed-Size: 477
Depends: erlang-base, erlang-crypto, erlang-xmerl, erlang-syntax-tools
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/mochi/mochiweb
Description: Erlang library for building lightweight HTTP servers
 MochiWeb is an Erlang library for building lightweight HTTP servers.
 .
 It is used (in conjunction with eswf and egeoip) to power services such as
 MochiBot and MochiAds, which serve dynamically generated SWF content to
 millions of viewers daily.
